NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ReadmeFromPod - Automatically convert POD to a
    README for Dist::Zilla

SYNOPSIS
        # dist.ini
        [ReadmeFromPod]

DESCRIPTION
    Generates a plain-text README for your Dist::Zilla powered dist from its
    "main_module" with Pod::Text.

